			<h2>About Bari Eye Hospital</h2>
			<p>Bari Eye Hospital is a leading eye care center committed to
				providing exceptional eye care services to patients of all ages. Our
				experienced team of ophthalmologists, optometrists, and support
				staff is dedicated to preserving and improving the vision of our
				patients.</p>
			<p>With state-of-the-art facilities and cutting-edge technology,
				we offer a comprehensive range of eye care services, including
				routine eye exams, cataract surgery, LASIK vision correction,
				treatment of eye diseases, and more.</p>
			<p>At Bari Eye Hospital, patient satisfaction is our top
				priority. We strive to ensure that every patient receives
				personalized care and attention in a compassionate and comfortable
				environment.</p>
			<p>Our mission is to enhance and protect the gift of sight, and
				we are committed to serving the community with integrity,
				excellence, and innovation in eye care.</p>

			<!-- Hospital History -->
			<h3>Our History</h3>
			<p>Founded in 1996, Bari Eye Hospital has a rich history of
				providing outstanding eye care services to the community. It was
				established by Dr. Prafulla Bari, a renowned ophthalmologist, with
				the vision of creating a world-class eye care facility.</p>
			<p>Over the years, the hospital has grown and evolved, embracing
				the latest advancements in eye care technology and expanding its
				team of skilled professionals. Today, we are a leading eye care
				center in the region, serving thousands of patients every year.</p>
			<p>Our commitment to excellence and compassionate care has earned
				us the trust and respect of our patients and the medical community.
				We continue to strive for excellence and remain dedicated to
				improving the vision and quality of life for our patients.</p>
